data.description: All new and ready to move in! Tastefully and completely renovated on a quarter acre lot with City Water! All wood plank ceramic tile floors, Quartz countertops, New Roof, New appliances, cabinets, windows, doors, quartz countertops, Air conditioner, trim and hardware. Open floor plan with spacious great room. Master has double vanity and large walk-in shower. Generous, private, tranquil back yard.
